verbose_text: As shown in Figure XREF_FIG, combined application of volatile SA (at 37.5-45.0 mM) and ITZ (2-3 mug mL -1, incorporated into SDA media) completely inhibited the growth of A. fumigatus AF293, while individual treatment of each compound, alone, allowed fungal growth.
evidence: SA (at 37.5-45.0 mM) and ITZ (2-3 mug mL -1 , incorporated into SDA media) completely inhibited the growth of A. fumigatus AF293
